          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " turned us on to an impressive collection of 1980s supercars that would have fit right in to an episode about everyone's favorite vice cops taking down a drug kingpin.",
            "type": "text",
